    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "This is a trial of up to 6-months duration for safety, tolerability, clinical efficacy assessments, PK and biomarkers analysis in breast carcinoma patients with secondary lymphoedema",
      "detailedDescription": "This trial will utilize a randomised, double-blinded, placebo controlled design that will assess the safety, tolerability, and secondarily clinical efficacy of LYT-100 over a period of up to 6-months of dosing in breast carcinoma patients with secondary lymphoedema following sentinel lymph node biopsy and/or axillary node dissection, with or without radiation."
    },
